"17c6aec98431eb383ddbe4afe9abe08912ab3b82","tid":36564,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你住邊<br />\n<br />\n住屯門七千<br />\n<br />\n住沙田萬二<br />\n<br />\n差好遠</blockquote><br />\n天水圍就有機"},{"pid":"0946e0eba0dc3489ea0c39d838ed3ca80fe4f6b5","tid":36564,"uid":10220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持旅行結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做起上黎仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c424eb9a44978187cdb45adaa227ccfdf000cb","tid":36564,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持旅行結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都支持但唔知使費幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8db5354dec3c2a87d9cdb827a8c3ea7212d403c","tid":36564,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n禮服果度<br />\n出門入門我地中式 去尖沙咀租褂用左$1500<br />\n自己出去造套西裝$1000<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老婆就係淘寶淘番黎 $500以內</span><br />\n老婆化妝$1500<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句睇咗3次"},{"pid":"5bd6f844b754774a9d4b119f885655b3b8e9ebbb","tid":36564,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"唔擺酒得唔得"},{"pid":"eb8660e0ea399ef10feda1c9792e88c031efd858","tid":36564,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"同男朋友講好求婚戒指+互送婚戒+簽紙算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af15c7c8410adc9084f88cffb7c4c343e47507ab","tid":36564,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n禮服果度<br />\n出門入門我地中式 去尖沙咀租褂用左$1500<br />\n自己出去造套西裝$1000<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老婆就係淘寶淘番黎 $500以內</span><br />\n老婆化妝$1500<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句睇咗3次</blockquote><br />\n笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淘寶淘老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9b4266c7472042e67453843fae4b7341526a52","tid":36564,"uid":56678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三年幾前搬出黎住，首期裝修雜費約55萬。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前結婚，影相禮金酒席細攪十幾圍，所有嘢加埋廿幾萬，收人情cover晒。<br />\n<br />\n之後蜜月旅行7-8萬。<br />\n<br />\n燒銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n55萬首期裝修雜費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到咁抵"},{"pid":"da89b7f74cff99253d2b6feaa2931de6649ab565","tid":36564,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三年幾前搬出黎住，首期裝修雜費約55萬。<br />\n<br />\n兩年前結婚，影相禮金酒席細攪十幾圍，所有嘢加埋廿幾萬，收人情cover晒。<br />\n<br />\n之後蜜月旅行7-8萬。<br />\n<br />\n燒銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n55萬首期裝修雜費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到咁抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首期裝修 $5x? 住邊區"},{"pid":"ac02de39f0746d5ec1b59617b92d38a6c8177a5d","tid":36564,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：四大長老都係好傳統...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cace92e1538927a701a3ed965e8ca658df93488c","tid":36564,"uid":1018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"咁多人都有擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想擺 我驚請晒我要請既人都坐唔到一圍"},{"pid":"0a624571ea65e6513bbae3a654161fda5dfd8597","tid":36564,"uid":18741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"本來有共識唔擺酒,男家亦都話唔想擺<br />\n女家個面話要擺,最尾我屋企人話最多用舊錢塞住外家把口<br />\n好過日後有說話聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左奶奶加外母同條裙褂去租其餘D衫同姊妹裙全部淘寶<br />\n租衫個到只係用左$3000<br />\n淘寶D裙大慨$4000左右<br />\n自己著個套禮服起中環是但整左一套千靚蚊<br />\n影相影左兩次,一次起STUDIO一次起街,兩次加埋用左13000<br />\n過大禮俾左88000,加埋餅卡濕碎野大約10萬左右<br />\n擺酒起尖沙咀到擺,平均一圍連埋酒水8200蚊圍<br />\n再自己訂埋D烈酒同紅酒同啤酒個到大約1萬到<br />\n男女家收返黎人情找完酒樓條數有3萬幾賺左<br />\n最後個3萬找埋D大酒同紅酒淨左既錢俾埋女家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實當自己賺左金器<br />\n老婆個面有錢親戚多,全部都有送金同鑽石,個到我諗拎去溶都袋返十幾萬,同有條2萬蚊鑽石手鏈<br />\nBTW:求完婚買左樓先擺酒結婚"},{"pid":"7544690b15a95cf110bb27068dc0a756ffc9092b","tid":36564,"uid":18741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多人都有擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想擺 我驚請晒我要請既人都坐唔到一圍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請我我幫你鄧腳<br />\n不過講明我做份人情係份東方日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}